{"id": "ChIJ05gry4t_hYAR4tpX79itpGo", "rating": 4.9, "userRatingCount": 58, "displayName": {"text": "Sun Moon Studio", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ05gry4t_hYAR4tpX79itpGo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCclJVZFNOMDlYWkZwT1JsOWpWR0ZHU21FeFRIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This place truly deserves its star. Every dish we tried was deceptively simple yet layered with complexity and intention. The dashi egg custard tart was one of the best bites I’ve had in a long time; I could have easily eaten a dozen. Exceptional food, attentive service, and an all-around a memorable dinner.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This place truly deserves its star. Every dish we tried was deceptively simple yet layered with complexity and intention. The dashi egg custard tart was one of the best bites I’ve had in a long time; I could have easily eaten a dozen. Exceptional food, attentive service, and an all-around a memorable dinner.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Steph Kwan", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107341064522484952638/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiSR4MoLPvFxd6pKM5SU46_oby8UjUTjjlD_AFyDUeIx185veZ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-01T01:28:26.204898213Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCclJVZFNOMDlYWkZwT1JsOWpWR0ZHU21FeFRIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCclJVZFNOMDlYWkZwT1JsOWpWR0ZHU21FeFRIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857f8bcb2b98d3:0x6aa4add8ef57dae2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ05gry4t_hYAR4tpX79itpGo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxdVVEVk5kMlpWUzJKTWQwRjNkWGxNTVVwc1kyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Sun Moon Studio has been our best restaurant experience in the Bay Area, period. They deserve all the hype and credit. Their food is simply amazing. They are very kind; the service is extra attentive and warm, not at all stuffy or pretentious.\n\nWe can't wait to visit again (just need to score those reservations!)", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Sun Moon Studio has been our best restaurant experience in the Bay Area, period. They deserve all the hype and credit. Their food is simply amazing. They are very kind; the service is extra attentive and warm, not at all stuffy or pretentious.\n\nWe can't wait to visit again (just need to score those reservations!)", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Miguel Ferrer", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106413794763348443657/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQVUp16NFJ48rAMrefidgyOdkBEsKnYVHAWkSVNE11RK-P98HJCg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-04T04:59:59.682221748Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxdVVEVk5kMlpWUzJKTWQwRjNkWGxNTVVwc1kyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxdVVEVk5kMlpWUzJKTWQwRjNkWGxNTVVwc1kyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857f8bcb2b98d3:0x6aa4add8ef57dae2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ05gry4t_hYAR4tpX79itpGo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2twWFZpMXlURTFUUWs1eVdFc3RZMmx2VVU1WGJtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "10 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Reservation is hard to make since they only have a few tables. But it’s definitely worth the effort of getting a table. The food is not only just great but also tailored well. It absolutely deserves the star, and the dinner experience can definitely beat lots of starred restaurants around the San Francisco Bay Area.\nWe especially love the egg tart with trout roe, the quail, the corn pasta, the squash shrimp tempura (just too many to be listed in this short paragraph ). And all the fruits they used are also fresh and taste good.\nAlso as a Taiwanese, I must say that I’m definitely intrigued by (and also proud of) seeing the inclusion of Taiwanese sausage in this dish. And it also tastes really good.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Reservation is hard to make since they only have a few tables. But it’s definitely worth the effort of getting a table. The food is not only just great but also tailored well. It absolutely deserves the star, and the dinner experience can definitely beat lots of starred restaurants around the San Francisco Bay Area.\nWe especially love the egg tart with trout roe, the quail, the corn pasta, the squash shrimp tempura (just too many to be listed in this short paragraph ). And all the fruits they used are also fresh and taste good.\nAlso as a Taiwanese, I must say that I’m definitely intrigued by (and also proud of) seeing the inclusion of Taiwanese sausage in this dish. And it also tastes really good.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "YCD", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112438514704128092304/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDHlbSzFM0wQYLcr6SQv2hfyQjnP6eCtwCwK7Tio8mvCiddn4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-08-25T05:48:20.762498907Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2twWFZpMXlURTFUUWs1eVdFc3RZMmx2VVU1WGJtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2twWFZpMXlURTFUUWs1eVdFc3RZMmx2VVU1WGJtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857f8bcb2b98d3:0x6aa4add8ef57dae2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ05gry4t_hYAR4tpX79itpGo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCUWFETTBTUzFoZFhWdGN6WjFNRVZYTVdwMGMwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Sun Moon Studio absolutely exceeded every expectation I had. This recently Michelin-starred gem showcases why Oakland's dining scene is truly world-class. The intimate setting makes you feel like you're part of their culinary space rather than just dining out.\n\nAlan Hsu and Sarah Cooper have created something truly special here. Their farmer and producer-driven approach isn't just a buzzword concept, but it's evident in every perfectly executed dish on their tasting menu. What impressed me most was how each ingredient, while part of a cohesive whole, had its own moment to shine. For the menu we were served, the young ginger brought the perfect heat and brightness to the soy milk tofu, the cured tomato elevated the black cod to new heights, and the buttery soft apricots paired with equally tender short ribs were nothing short of sublime. The menu is constantly rotating based on the seasons and what is best and I'm sure it will blow you away.\n\nWhat also stood out was their thoughtful approach to beverages, with an excellent selection of non-alcoholic options for those who don't drink. They're also fantastic at accommodating dietary restrictions without compromising the experience.\n\nPractical notes: Book at least 6 weeks in advance (reservations fill up quickly!)", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Sun Moon Studio absolutely exceeded every expectation I had. This recently Michelin-starred gem showcases why Oakland's dining scene is truly world-class. The intimate setting makes you feel like you're part of their culinary space rather than just dining out.\n\nAlan Hsu and Sarah Cooper have created something truly special here. Their farmer and producer-driven approach isn't just a buzzword concept, but it's evident in every perfectly executed dish on their tasting menu. What impressed me most was how each ingredient, while part of a cohesive whole, had its own moment to shine. For the menu we were served, the young ginger brought the perfect heat and brightness to the soy milk tofu, the cured tomato elevated the black cod to new heights, and the buttery soft apricots paired with equally tender short ribs were nothing short of sublime. The menu is constantly rotating based on the seasons and what is best and I'm sure it will blow you away.\n\nWhat also stood out was their thoughtful approach to beverages, with an excellent selection of non-alcoholic options for those who don't drink. They're also fantastic at accommodating dietary restrictions without compromising the experience.\n\nPractical notes: Book at least 6 weeks in advance (reservations fill up quickly!)", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Emily Xie", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113481516027020177390/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVc5cXaMfQPI8PFOKw6abZSpp7Pz2y8wQRKFY6d1_lDBDTqTWvygw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-07-12T14:08:11.495622782Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCUWFETTBTUzFoZFhWdGN6WjFNRVZYTVdwMGMwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCUWFETTBTUzFoZFhWdGN6WjFNRVZYTVdwMGMwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f8bcb2b98d3:0x6aa4add8ef57dae2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ05gry4t_hYAR4tpX79itpGo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2toaU9FSmliQzFUTFZWcFduQjRZVzk1Y2xOdlpWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Recently went there for dinner after wanting to go for SO LONG and I am so tempted to just make another reservation to go again!\n\nEverything was absolutely delicious. No notes! Except I wish they also had a bakery so I could just order the dashi egg tart with roe and lapchong brioche anytime I wanted.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Recently went there for dinner after wanting to go for SO LONG and I am so tempted to just make another reservation to go again!\n\nEverything was absolutely delicious. No notes! Except I wish they also had a bakery so I could just order the dashi egg tart with roe and lapchong brioche anytime I wanted.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tiffany Oda", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103656227235151003404/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUl86MNIjPLv0yFBIktPimfokjuZj95GvuhQzsanz2Agy62jbmD=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-01T00:24:36.836889329Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2toaU9FSmliQzFUTFZWcFduQjRZVzk1Y2xOdlpWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2toaU9FSmliQzFUTFZWcFduQjRZVzk1Y2xOdlpWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857f8bcb2b98d3:0x6aa4add8ef57dae2"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJ05gry4t_hYAR4tpX79itpGo/photos/AWCwydhnUAOywghU8ZPlG4wa5etrQ1adynQZFenh_NGTLT3smFq_FqpTSuC7OwH4mgj2LaPxyOXaO5M0VPkjiOnSsarA9nfSXGRFNAbOywwBtsEsqAl28Bc91V_bJ3d72hXc6NrhcI0TU46M6K2Ns3SCY1ui6mYh2h6ufmY0atEV57ezXW22q5SCj-TgEx7hNP6dipYbomI7NfeA1oqUgv07pCMZC2w3UEM0KR8xaN7L88ZZWnqYkMmhnT34EQgnUSXF96ERuqicp7l0lo5iwiJBSCSDGtNinSxBLlMlnIjl4C5CeJzsUx1tmkX98N8zBSf2saHGjtrDceO9Ufvebx0oaPqe9nbFwiiLjL2ERfvXiCUAyVIgrsWq2SCh1HO5b6L5VfQdo5jDjGF-W93fTEOojFrYpPoTGrkfQpYvaVLnTexNY8k3X_5MNTOUHmFOFkPK", "widthPx": 4000, "heightPx": 3000, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Kathleen Chen", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/106252575500768103982", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlpNP5Nh1CpxQ75RhDuMvBaMmJ2qs-glQCDGYjuHSwMuTg2QAL_w=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIABIhDwYWS1WQFhAFTkxcyen7GF&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&hl=en-US", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!3m4!1e2!3m2!1sCIABIhDwYWS1WQFhAFTkxcyen7GF!2e10!4m2!3m1!1s0x80857f8bcb2b98d3:0x6aa4add8ef57dae2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ05gry4t_hYAR4tpX79itpGo/photos/AWCwydhDQXzEXFvxofVnADjF0xTzWWHnZtkuJMMCaJurC5AIdSq